===Adjective===
'''over'''
# [[finished]]; [[ended]] or [[concluded]]
#:''The show is '''over'''.''
# Through with; emotionally detatched.
#:''He is finally '''over''' his ex-girlfriend.''
# ''(as a prefix):'' to [[excess]].
#:''He is '''over-'''zealous...''
#:''The latest policy was '''over-'''conservative...''

